TextEng: Are you a prisoner here?
Stand back! I'll have no tricks out of you!
No, I'm certainly not one of the cultists.
You kept in prison?
Stand back! No tricks!!
Me not cultist, no.
How do I know that this isn't some ruse?
Text: 이게 속임수가 아니란 걸 어떻게 알지?

TextEng: I'd appreciate some information, first.
What reward would I get for letting you go?
Would you be able to find your way out on your own?
Text: 혼자서 나갈 길을 찾을 수 있어?

TextEng: I'm not here to rescue you.
How I know you not lying?
Text: 네가 거짓말 안 하는 거 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: Me have questions, first.
Is there reward for letting you go?
You find way out on own?
Me no rescuer.
I never said that. You could betray me... I'll have to kill you.
Text: 그런 말 안 했어. 날 배신할 수도 있잖아... 죽여야겠군.

TextEng: Yes, go on. I've got better things to do, here.
Text: 그래, 가. 여기서 할 일이 더 있거든.

TextEng: I don't know. Is there anything in it for me for helping you?
Text: 글쎄. 널 도우면 내게 뭐가 좋은데?

TextEng: Never say that. You coulds betray me... me has to kill you.
Text: 그런 말 안 했어. 너 나 배신할 수 있어... 나 너 죽여야 해.

TextEng: Yes, you go. Me has better things to do.
Text: 응, 너 가. 나 할 일 더 있어.

TextEng: Don't know. What in it for me?
I don't trust you. Time to die!
Text: 널 믿을 수 없어. 죽을 시간이야!

TextEng: No believe! Die! Die!!
Yes, I could use some information.
You're of no use to me, then.
Yes, tell me. That good.
You no use to me, then.
Then you're free to go.
Why don't you join me, then? I intend to stop Maugrim, myself.
Text: 그럼 나와 함께하지 않을래? 나도 모그림을 막으러 가는 중이야.

TextEng: Then you go now.
Maybe you joins me, then? Me go to stop Maugrim now.
Text: 그럼 나랑 같이 갈래? 나 지금 모그림 막으러 가.

TextEng: What happened here in the tower?
Text: 이 탑에서 무슨 일이 있었던 거야?

TextEng: How does one get around this place?
Tell me what you know about the cult.
All right. I'm done with the questions.
What happen in tower?
How you gets around tower?
What you knows about cult?
Me done with questions.
I can't trust you not to betray me. Sorry, but you die.
Text: 날 배신 안 할 거라고 믿을 수 없어. 미안하지만, 죽어야겠어.

TextEng: Me not trusts you not to betray. You die, now.
Text: 나 너 배신 안 할 거라고 안 믿어. 너 지금 죽어.

TextEng: You're free to go. Or you could help me fight Maugrim.
Text: 가도 좋아. 아니면 나랑 모그림이랑 싸울 수도 있고.

TextEng: You free to go. Or you coulds help me fight Maugrim.
Text: 너 가도 돼. 아니면 나랑 모그림 싸워도 되고.

TextEng: Why not join me and fight Maugrim?
Maybe you joins me and fight Maugrim?
How did Maugrim manage to take over?
Text: 모그림이 어떻게 장악할 수 있었던 거야?

TextEng: What does he want the Tower for?
Who is this Arklem? Do you know where he is?
Text: 이 아클렘이 누군데? 어디 있는지 알아?

TextEng: The fighting appears to be still ongoing.
Text: 싸움이 아직 진행 중인 것 같은데.

TextEng: I want to know something else.
How Maugrim take over tower?
What he wants wizard tower for?
Who Arklem? You knows where he be?
Fightings still goes on here, me thinks.
Text: 싸움 아직 계속되는 것 같아, 내 생각에.

TextEng: Me want to know something else.
What is this power that he worships?
What is he looking for?
What this power he worship?
What he looks for?
What do they want?
Tell me about Maugrim.
Who are Maugrim's supporters, here?
Where do I find Maugrim?
I want to know something else.
What they want?
Tells me 'bout Maugrim.
Who is Maugrim's supporters?
Where me finds Maugrim?
Me wants to know something else.
Why would you tell me that?
So you won't help me, then?
Then forget it. Leave, while you can.
Text: 그럼 됐어. 갈 수 있을 때 가.

TextEng: Why you tells me that?
So you not help me, then?
Then forgets it. You leave quick.
Then I am forced to kill you, I guess.
Text: 그렇다면, 어쩔 수 없이 널 죽여야겠군.

TextEng: Then me forced to kill you.
Text: 그럼 나 어쩔 수 없이 너 죽여야 해.

TextEng: Who be this Valinda?
Who is Valinda Shadowmantle?
